Class MainSceneController

java.lang.Object
eason.taskC482.MainSceneController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class MainSceneController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
This is the controller for the main FXML file. It handles movement to other windows, and the TableViews for the Parts and Products, as well as their deletion.

      public void onDeleteProduct()
      This method handles deletion of a product. Checks are in place to ensure a product is currently selected, the user confirms that they want to delete, and that the product does not have any associated parts.
